### 🛡️ 2. Payment Control & Verified PDF
We will transition from "Loose Permissions" to a "Verified Financial System".

#### [NEW] [011_payment_audit_and_permissions.sql](file:///d:/GT%20CRM%20WEB%20PROJECT/gtgroupcrmproject/supabase/migrations/011_payment_audit_and_permissions.sql)
- **Role-Based Access**:
    - **Couselor/Receptionist**: Can "Add" payments but cannot see global revenue or "Edit" existing ones.
    - **Office Manager**: Can edit office payments.
    - **Super Admin**: Full global visibility.
- **Audit Logging**: Create a `payment_history` table to track every modification made to a payment record.

#### [MODIFY] [Student Payments Detail](file:///d:/GT%20CRM%20WEB%20PROJECT/gtgroupcrmproject/src/app/students/[id]/page.jsx)
- **Revenue Protection**: Hide total revenue from staff members.
- **PDF Download**: Add a button: **"Download Service Verified Copy"**.
- This will generate a professional PDF with your **Global Logo**, Student details, and Verfied Stamp using `jspdf`.

